snippet.title: Police Shootout - Release Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
👮 | Police Shootout is NOW available to PLAY on Steam! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1279240/Police_Shootout/

🚨 Police Shootout is a new turn-based FPS game! 🚔 Solve cases and gain experience, but also find out why a good young policeman gave up his career in a big city and moved to a small town of San Adrino. 👮‍♀️

#PoliceShootout #Police #cops
